title: Terminally-Ill Genius Dark Knight
summary: Terminally-Ill Genius Dark Knight Manhwa is a fantasy RPG infamous for its extreme difficulty. However, to Yoo Chan, who was diagnosed with a terminal illness at a young age, this game was his entire life and has now become his reality. From now on, Yoo Chan has to survive in this world as Nox von Reinharber, the worst villain in the first act of the game. Will he be able to reach the end of the story safely? 시한부 천재 암흑기사, Time-Limited Genius Dark Knight
